main event: A witness flying over Benghazi observed a bright white round object moving at high speed on 16 Feb 1959.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 15 seconds,The object was described as larger than an average light and very bright,The object disappeared suddenly without making any sound,The witness reported feeling scared after the sighting,The report is classified as insufficient data.
witness description: The witness was flying at 2,000 ft and observed the object much higher.
